{"bloom_level": "create", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00064", "completion": "After completing this week, you will be able to: TO-02: Design reusable RDF vocabularies using RDF Schema to declare classes, properties, domains, ranges, and subclass or subproperty hierarchies that support lightweight inference. CO-07: Declare RDFS classes and properties using rdfs:Class , rdf:Property , rdfs:domain , and rdfs:range , and justify vocabulary naming choices. Learners should be able to generate a fresh example or application of total time.", "content_type": "introduction", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_8f936deac11f767f", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["to-02", "co-07", "co-08", "co-09"], "prompt": "Design a short activity that teaches total time to a learner new to the material.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 80, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00064", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00064]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.3, "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s3"}], "template_id": "create._default"}
