{"bloom_level": "create", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00048", "completion": "Open conf.ttl and write the prefix block: @prefix rdf: , @prefix rdfs: , @prefix dc: , @prefix foaf: , plus the conference's own @prefix conf: . For each domain entity, decide: reuse-as-is (use the existing IRI directly), reuse-with-subclass (mint a new IRI as rdfs:subClassOf the reused term), or new (mint a new IRI as a direct subclass of rdfs:Resource ). A proficient learner can generate a fresh example or application of inventory the domain.", "content_type": "procedure", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_90027baf4bf7ecef", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["to-02", "co-09"], "prompt": "Design a simplified variant of the procedure for inventory the domain suitable for a beginner.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 64, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00048", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00048]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.3, "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s3"}], "template_id": "create.procedure"}
