{"bloom_level": "apply", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00093", "completion": "This self-check is formative — it is not graded. :Motorcycle — subclass of :Vehicle ; will appear in the disjointness axiom for :Car but otherwise has no OWL-2 axioms. Even though no OWL-2 axiom is asserted about :Motorcycle directly, it appears as the operand of the disjointness axiom on :Car , so it must be an OWL-2 class for that axiom to be valid. Learners should be able to use this about rdfs3 in a new but similar situation.", "content_type": "page-title", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_2d2d999285337aee", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["co-08", "co-23", "to-02", "to-06"], "prompt": "Use the idea of rdfs3 to resolve a realistic problem; describe both the problem and your approach.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 109, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00093", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00093]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.65, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s4"}], "template_id": "apply._default"}
