{"bloom_level": "apply", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00106", "completion": "To make the example concrete, we will use a small Turtle dataset describing three employees and the companies they work for. PREFIX foaf: PREFIX ex: SELECT ?person ?personName ?companyName WHERE { ?person a foaf:Person ; foaf:name ?personName ; ex:worksFor ?company . A proficient learner can use this about rdf in a new but similar situation.", "content_type": "page-title", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_b9da6dc0ecc5a518", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["co-11", "to-03"], "prompt": "Use the idea of rdf to resolve a realistic problem; describe both the problem and your approach.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 122, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00106", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00106]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.85, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:sparql11_query_accessible#997ebaa48b8c921b"}, {"confidence": 0.7, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "contributing", "sourceId": "dart:sparql11_query_accessible#2da0210f90dacd30"}], "template_id": "apply._default"}
