{"bloom_level": "understand", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00128", "completion": "Real linked-data deployments are not single graphs. A typical knowledge-graph application has a private domain graph (customer master data, internal vocabulary), one or more enterprise reference graphs (product catalog, organizational chart), and one or more public open-data sources (Wikidata, DBpedia, GeoNames, schema.org). Learners should be able to explain this about latency in their own words. [rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00128]", "content_type": "explanation", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_353a233f79b7ea15", "instruction_variant": 2, "lo_refs": ["co-15", "co-09", "to-03", "to-02"], "prompt": "Give a source-grounded answer: Explain in your own words what latency means and why it matters. Cite the source chunk in brackets.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": true, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 200144, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00128", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00128]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.85, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s6"}], "template_id": "understand.explanation"}
{"bloom_level": "evaluate", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00129", "completion": "Federated queries pay three costs that single-graph queries do not. Internalize all three before deploying federation in production: Latency. Learners should be able to judge the quality of claims about latency against clear criteria.", "content_type": "explanation", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_30fcc41ab9f96a91", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["co-15", "to-03"], "prompt": "Evaluate whether the core claim about latency is well supported, and say what would strengthen it.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 145, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00129", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00129]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.85, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s6"}], "template_id": "evaluate.explanation"}
