{"bloom_level": "understand", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00205", "completion": "RDFS lets you name classes; OWL 2 lets you define them. Once you have it, an OWL 2 reasoner can classify instance data: anyone who is a Woman and has at least one :hasChild assertion will be derived to be a Mother automatically, and anyone explicitly typed as Mother will be derived to be a Woman with at least one child. A proficient learner can explain this about defined class in their own words. [rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00205]", "content_type": "motivation", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_80766315980af5bd", "instruction_variant": 2, "lo_refs": ["co-24", "to-06"], "prompt": "Give a source-grounded answer: Explain the core idea behind defined class for a learner new to the topic. Cite the source chunk in brackets.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": true, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 200221, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00205", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00205]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.3, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s9"}], "template_id": "understand._default"}
{"bloom_level": "understand", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00206", "completion": "Asserting :marie a :Woman plus :marie :hasChild :alice entails :marie a :Mother ; asserting :marie a :Mother entails :marie a :Woman and :marie :hasChild [something]. If you instead used rdfs:subClassOf here, you would lose half the inference: instances asserted as Woman with a child would not be derived to be Mothers, only the other direction. A proficient learner can explain this about defined class in their own words.", "content_type": "motivation", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_e6a1ad3bf1563bb0", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["co-24", "to-06"], "prompt": "Explain the core idea behind defined class for a learner new to the topic.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 222, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00206", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00206]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.3, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s9"}], "template_id": "understand._default"}
