{"bloom_level": "understand", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00247", "completion": "For pipeline-style integration the most common OWL 2 profile choice is OWL 2 RL , and it is worth understanding why. Recall the three profiles from Week 10: EL targets large terminological classification (e.g. SNOMED CT), QL targets ontology-based data access by query rewriting, and RL targets rule-based materialization on top of an RDF graph store. Learners should be able to explain this about ingest in their own words.", "content_type": "explanation", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_f885a8e2a3051b1d", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["co-25", "to-06"], "prompt": "Explain in your own words what ingest means and why it matters.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 263, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00247", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00247]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.8, "extractor": "source-router", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s11"}], "template_id": "understand.explanation"}
