{"bloom_level": "create", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00275", "completion": "Once the layers are clear, the pipeline almost designs itself. Stage 1 is ingestion : source data arrives in some non-RDF form (CSV, JSON, a relational database, an XML feed, a domain-specific format) and an emitter component transforms it into RDF triples in a known serialization. Learners should be able to generate a fresh example or application of ingestion. [rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00275]", "content_type": "explanation", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_178c18aecaec239b", "instruction_variant": 2, "lo_refs": ["co-27", "co-10", "co-19", "to-07", "to-02", "to-04"], "prompt": "Give a source-grounded answer: Propose a new explanation or analogy for ingestion that would help a novice learner. Cite the source chunk in brackets.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": true, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 200291, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00275", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00275]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.8, "extractor": "source-router", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s12"}], "template_id": "create.explanation"}
{"bloom_level": "create", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00273", "completion": "Week 12 · CO-27 (architect) · Synthesis review across Weeks 1–11 The single most useful mental model for the capstone deliverable is to see the semantic web stack as four composing layers, not as four competing tools. The vocabulary layer is RDFS plus OWL 2 — the classes, properties, and axioms that describe what those triples mean. A proficient learner can generate a fresh example or application of ingestion.", "content_type": "explanation", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_962f6503b1b5d8ab", "instruction_variant": 0, "lo_refs": ["co-27", "co-18", "to-07", "to-04"], "prompt": "Propose a new explanation or analogy for ingestion that would help a novice learner.", "provider": "mock", "requires_source_citation": false, "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 289, "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00273", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00273]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.8, "extractor": "source-router", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s12"}], "template_id": "create.explanation"}
